  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV31">
<l>kālanēmi kālaṉē kaṇakkilāta kīrttiyāy</l>
<l>ñālamēḻu muṇṭupaṇṭō r pālaṉāya paṇpaṉē</l>
<l>vēlaivēva vilvaḷaitta velciṉatta vīraniṉ</l>
<l>pālarāya pattarcittam mutticeyyum mūrttiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Death of Kālanemi! O You of innumerable glories!</l>
<l>O courteous [Lord] who became a unique child previously,</l>
<l rend="indent">having swallowed the seven worlds!</l>
<l>O warrior with a conquering anger that consists in bending the bow</l>
<l rend="indent">So that the ocean burned!</l>
<l>O Lord who give liberation as per the intentions of the devotees</l>
<l rend="indent">who are on Your side!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
